Chain.Food grants to the User a non-exclusive, non-transferable, revocable license to use the Platform solely for personal or commercial purposes in accordance with the terms and conditions of this Agreement.

2. Platform Use
The User shall use the Platform solely for the purpose of exchanging information about free food, obtaining Foodcoin tokens, publishing "empty plate" posts, and redeeming rewards from partner merchants. The User shall comply with all applicable local food safety regulations and laws, and assume full responsibility for any actions or consequences resulting from their use of the Platform.

