The User acknowledges and accepts the risk of volatility in token transactions on the Platform, and shall assess the risks themselves and invest cautiously.

5. Non-Profit Donations
Chain.Food may donate tax revenue and profits earned from users obtaining FoodCoin and minting NFTs to non-profit organizations dedicated to donating food to underdeveloped regions and disaster-stricken areas. The act of donation does not mean that Chain.Food endorses or supports the organization.

6. Term and Termination
This Agreement shall remain in effect until terminated by either party. Chain.Food may terminate this Agreement at any time without cause or notice. Upon termination, the User shall immediately cease all use of the Platform.

7. Disclaimer of Warranties
The Platform is provided "as is" without warranty of any kind, express or implied, including, but not limited to, the warranties of merchantability, fitness for a particular purpose, and non-infringement.

8. Limitation of Liability
